      <td>15</td>
      <td>Reliability</td>
      <td>"Reliability" differs from the other four performances in that it is an operational performance. "Reliability" is how well your services meet user expectations, such as availability and performance.</td>
      <td>Debellis, D. (2022). 2022 Accelerate State of DevOps Report. DORA. Page 10.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
