      <td>A cloud-based tool is a software that uses cloud application technology to centrally store data and offer up-to-date information to all users. The data is frequently stored on faraway servers, and the program is frequently accessed online or through an app.</td>
      <td>Dutta, B. (2022). 10 Best Cloud-Based Tools in 2022. Analyticssteps. https://www.analyticssteps.com/blogs/best-cloud-based-tools</td>
    </tr>
